    text = "JUMP JETS\\\nAdvantages: Enables a 'Mech to fly over obstacles for short periods of time. Jump jets can clear most buildings and trees.\\\nDisadvantages: Generates high levels of heat. Only certain 'Mechs are equipped to handle jump jets."
